OL,3,CDoctors divided in Jersey's assisted
OL,4,Cdying debate
OL,6,FIf politicians pass a law to allow
OL,7,Fassisted dying, doctors will be a
OL,8,Fvital part of the process.
OL,10,FThose who opt into the scheme would
OL,11,Fhave the power to authorise and in
OL,12,Fsome cases give the lethal dose.
OL,14,FPoliticians with a final decision
OL,15,Fexpected this week.
OL,17,FHowever, there are deeply held views
OL,18,Fon both sides of the debate and the
OL,19,Fissue has split the medical community.
