OL,3,CDoctors divided in Jersey's assisted
OL,4,Cdying debate
OL,6,FDr Nigel Minihane is an experienced
OL,7,FJersey GP who is in favour of
OL,8,Flegalising assisted dying for people
OL,9,Fwith a terminal illness and has
OL,10,Fcreated a local group for like-minded
OL,11,Fhealthcare professionals.
OL,13,FHe says: "We're talking about autonomy
OL,14,Fhere, if someone wants to follow a
OL,15,Fparticular path then why shouldn't
OL,16,Fthey?
